<p>Always verify intent before writing. 5 minutes of SERP analysis prevents months of wasted effort on content that never ranks.</p>
<p><strong>Impact timeline:</strong> Immediate improvement in rankings after correcting format mismatches.</p>
<h2>Strategy 9: Optimize for Featured Snippets and AI Overviews</h2>
<p>Featured snippets appear above position 1. AI Overviews appear at the top of 30% of queries. Winning these positions drives traffic even as zero-click searches grow.</p>
<p><strong>How to win featured snippets:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Answer the query directly in 40 to 60 words at the top of the relevant section.</li>
<li>Use the exact question as an H2 or H3 heading.</li>
<li>Format answers as paragraphs (for definition queries), lists (for step queries), or tables (for comparison queries).</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>How to get cited in AI Overviews:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Structure content with clear headers and short paragraphs.</li>
<li>Include specific data points with sources.</li>
<li>Demonstrate <a href="/blog/eeat-google-quality-guide/">E-E-A-T</a> signals (author credentials, firsthand experience, citations).</li>
<li>Build topical authority through content clusters.</li>
</ul>
<p>Read our guide on <a href="/blog/optimize-google-ai-overviews/">optimizing for Google AI Overviews</a> and <a href="/blog/get-cited-ai-search/">getting cited in AI search</a> for the full optimization process.</p>
<p><strong>Impact timeline:</strong> 4 to 8 weeks for snippet acquisition after optimization.</p>
